  "description": "<div>\n<h4>Application:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>1986-1992 Chevrolet Camaro with SBC V8 Engines</li>\n<li>1982-1992 Pontiac Firebird / Trans Am with SBC V8 Engines</li>\n<li>1964-1973 Chevrolet Chevelle with SBC V8 Engines</li>\n<li>1964-1987 Chevrolet El Camino with SBC V8 Engines</li>\n<li>Side Mount Application on Chevy / Pontiac 283 - 400 Cu. In. Chevy Small Block SBC V8 Engines</li>\n<li>For twin turbos setup; NOT direct fit</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Features:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fits T3 Turbo Flange, 24.5\" total length</li>\n<li>Excellent quality and durability to improve vehicle performance; engineered to be bolt-on replacement for easy installation</li>\n<li>Tubular manifold design with better exhaust flow, delivers more top-end power</li>\n<li>Precision aligned tubes made of 16-gauge 304 stainless steel</li>\n<li>Head flanges laser-cut from high-quality 7/16-inch thick steel plates</li>\n<li>Flange flattened by hydraulic press for precise, leak-free sealing</li>\n<li>All joints golden color TIG brass style welded to prevent cracking and wear</li>\n<li>Flanges chrome plated for corrosion resistance</li>\n<li>Polished surface for extra protection against rust</li>\n<li>Accessories shown in main photo are included</li>\n<li>1-year warranty for any manufacturing defect</li>\n<li>No instructions provided; professional installation recommended</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Technical Specifications:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Manifold Type: Twin Turbo Manifold</li>\n<li>Runner Diameter: 1-5/8 in. (42mm)</li>\n<li>Turbo Fitment: T3</li>\n<li>Turbo Mount Position: Side Mount</li>\n<li>Head Flange Thickness: 7/16 in. (11.5mm)</li>\n<li>Pipe Thickness: 16 gauge (1.5mm)</li>\n<li>Material: 304 Stainless Steel</li>\n<li>Finish: Polished</li>\n</ul>\n</div>",
